The Dead body of a 100 Level female chemical engineering student of the University of Port Harcourt (Uniport) was today discovered by her course mate in her room at Aluu, Rivers State. According to source her course mate came to find out why she didn’t come to class because attendance was taken and she wasn’t taking her calls. So on getting there, she saw her door locked and she peeped through the window and saw the girl laying dead, she raised alarm and people gathered to break the door. Lo and behold, they saw sniper on the floor and dried blood on her face. The lodge occupants said they saw her last on Saturday. Probably she might have died since Saturday night and only discovered today been Monday. According to reports by friends, the young girl identified as Hikmat Gbadamosi has been battling with depression for a very long time. Source: nairaland